=======
CLASS 3
=======

* box model:
  |---margin
  |---border
  |---padding

* With position='absolute', calculating top, left, bottom, right etc. is called as 'magic number'. Doing this is a bad practice, because it may tear the website in other devices.

* div has no property. it is completely clean.

* pseudo

* flex-direction: row (or) 

* flexbox creates axis:
	align-items: center; // would align along cross axis
	justify-items: center; // would align along primary axis